import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react";
import LoadingBar from "../LoadingBar/LoadingBar";
import {
  Isprobaj,
  IsprobajResults,
  IsprobajWrapper,
  LoadingBarTitle,
  IsprobajInput,
  IsprobajResultsContainer,
  InputTemperatura,
  Wind,
  WindType,
} from "./IsprobajElements";

function Test() {
  const [barPercentage, setbarPercentage] = useState(2000);

  return (
    <>
      <Isprobaj id="isprobaj">
        <IsprobajInput>
          <InputTemperatura
            placeholder="Temperatura"
            type="text"
          ></InputTemperatura>
          <InputTemperatura
            placeholder="Temperatura"
            type="text"
          ></InputTemperatura>
          <InputTemperatura
            placeholder="Temperatura"
            type="text"
          ></InputTemperatura>
          <Wind name="wind">
            <WindType value="wind1"></WindType>
            <WindType value="wind1"></WindType>
            <WindType value="wind1"></WindType>
          </Wind>
        </IsprobajInput>
        <IsprobajResultsContainer id="test1">
          <IsprobajResults>
            <IsprobajWrapper>
              <LoadingBarTitle>Temperature</LoadingBarTitle>
              <LoadingBar
                min_progress="0"
                max_progress="6000"
                title="Temperature"
                done={barPercentage}
              />
            </IsprobajWrapper>
            <IsprobajWrapper>
              <LoadingBarTitle>Temperature</LoadingBarTitle>
              <LoadingBar
                min_progress="0"
                max_progress="6000"
                title="Temperature"
                done={barPercentage}
              />
            </IsprobajWrapper>
            <IsprobajWrapper>
              <LoadingBarTitle>Temperature</LoadingBarTitle>
              <LoadingBar
                min_progress="0"
                max_progress="6000"
                title="Temperature"
                done={barPercentage}
              />
            </IsprobajWrapper>
            <IsprobajWrapper>
              <LoadingBarTitle>Temperature</LoadingBarTitle>
              <LoadingBar
                min_progress="0"
                max_progress="6000"
                title="Temperature"
                done={barPercentage}
              />
            </IsprobajWrapper>
            <IsprobajWrapper>
              <LoadingBarTitle>Temperature</LoadingBarTitle>
              <LoadingBar
                min_progress="0"
                max_progress="6000"
                title="Temperature"
                done={barPercentage}
              />
            </IsprobajWrapper>
          </IsprobajResults>
        </IsprobajResultsContainer>
      </Isprobaj>
    </>
  );
}

export default Test;
